{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"629222-demam-sebelum-ujian","title":"Demam Sebelum Ujian","description":"Ujian sebentar lagi, tetapi Ibu sedang demam. Semua orang di rumah cemas akan keadaan Ibu dan berusaha menyembuhkannya. Apakah demam itu akan reda sebelum ujian? ","language":"Bahasa Indonesia","langCode":"id","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Badan Bahasa Dyah Murti"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Badan Pengembangan dan Pembinaan Bahasa","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/629222-demam-sebelum-ujian"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727674/size3/8f8c33f70a4806d41efd626c5cf14df3.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727674/size6/8f8c33f70a4806d41efd626c5cf14df3.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673940/size6/64323183a320c4c974742f86639ad2f4.jpg","text":"Hanya tinggal empat hari,\nhari ujian sebentar lagi,\nketika demam Ibu terus meninggi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673941/size6/82e67f962df826cd55419659812e0aca.jpg","text":"Nenek membuat ramuan penurun demam, dan dia pun bernyanyi menenangkan.\nNamun, ujian itu sudah menjadi monster yang menyeramkan.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673942/size6/7a2196ed49e7836180b7f9582d877a9e.jpg","text":"Ayah mengompres dahi Ibu dengan kain basah.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673943/size6/551d274fec2dea20ab480480361c6d04.jpg","text":"Ayah menyisir rambut Ibu dan menyuapi Ibu dengan bubur khichdi karena ...","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673944/size6/8e47726d60b6b450fcc25224f580f0c2.jpg","text":"Ketika buku catatan dan belajar memenuhi hari-hari Ibu,\nmembuat naik darah,\nhingga demam Ibu makin parah.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673945/size6/08a09ac3f40d33cccbde90ca9d3ab14a.jpg","text":"Kakak membaca bab demi bab\ndari buku teks Ibu dengan lantang.\nDia bertanya,\"Bu, apakah ini bisa membuatmu senang?'.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673946/size6/1364ed53008954bd51eed09b92ef7bec.jpg","text":"\"Jangan takut, Bu,\" ucapku sambil menari seperti badut.\nAku menceritakan cerita lucu hingga Ibu tersenyum dan melupakan rasa takut.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673947/size6/06807af1a036281570e92526a3a14987.jpg","text":"Tak satu pun boleh menjenguk,\nbaik tetangga maupun teman,\nketika demam Ibu terus berkepanjangan.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673948/size6/9ce6c2f42bea8a942693892d9a864894.jpg","text":"Akhirnya, hari ujian pun tiba.\nIbu sudah sembuh dan kembali ceria.\nIbu tidak lagi cemas dan demam pun sudah reda.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673949/size6/176afa86807ac7171313165d488b594b.jpg","text":"Tahukan kalian semua?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673950/size6/cd9bf868a00ecdddccd1dba07aba90df.jpg","text":"Ibuku berhasil mendapatkan gelar sarjana!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673951/size6/d9c6a630ce185c1862b251be9f52ce04.jpg","text":"13/13","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":146}}